Class Log

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.java.com.djrapitops.plan.Log

  • public class Log
extends Object
    This class manages the messages going to the Console Logger.

    Methods of Abstract Plugin Framework log utility are used.

    Since:
    3.0.0
    Author:
    Rsl1122
